=begin rakudoc

=TITLE Changelog

=SUBTITLE User-visible changes by release

=head1 Overview

This changelog follows the shape of Keep a Changelog, adapted to Rakudoc.
Versions use the C<META6.json> version number and release tags use the
C<release-x.y.z> convention.

=head1 0.0.9 - 2026-07-02

=head2 Fixed

=item C<available-modules> now discovers installed modules from each
distribution's C<provides> metadata instead of using zef distribution names.
Plugin packages such as C<Qwiratry--Location--HTTP> are therefore visible to
glob discovery as C<Qwiratry::Location::HTTP>.

=head2 Changed

=item C<available-modules> documentation now describes installed discovery in
terms of distribution C<provides> entries rather than repository names alone.

=head2 Added

=item Private helper C<!installed-module-names> collects loadable module FQCNs
from installed distributions.

=item Tests in C<t/03-available-modules-tests.rakutest> cover lib-path discovery,
installed C<provides> naming, and glob discovery of installed plugin modules.

=end rakudoc
